FAQs
 What programs are offered at the First Faculty of Medicine, Charles University?
A: The First Faculty of Medicine, Charles University offers programs in General Medicine, Dentistry, and various postgraduate specializations.

 How can I apply to the First Faculty of Medicine, Charles University?
A: You can apply to the First Faculty of Medicine, Charles University through their online application portal, providing necessary documents and meeting specific entry requirements.

What are the admission requirements for the First Faculty of Medicine, Charles University?
A: Admission requirements include a high school diploma, proficiency in English, and passing an entrance exam in subjects like biology, chemistry, and physics.
